## ğŸš€ Why This Project
This project was intentionally built **without a framework** to showcase:
- Core knowledge of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
- Ability to manage state and UI updates without relying on external libraries.  
- Understanding of responsive design.  

ğŸ‘‰ In a real-world production environment, an application of this type would typically be developed with a **modern framework such as React, Vue, or Angular** for scalability, maintainability, and developer productivity.

